Perry Lyn DUPREE 71P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2017 Perry Lyn Dupree, for Dupree, Perry Lyn. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C.
